This bug applies to all panel macros.  Eg panel, info, code.
If a panel has a broken style declared, and the page it is on is edited in the Rich Text Editor, the content of the panel will be deleted.

The steps to reproduce the problem:
# Create a page containing the following:
{noformat}
{panel:borderStyle=solids|bgColor=#EEEEE0|borderColor=#3C78B5}
testing purpose
{panel}
{noformat}
Note that the borderStyle is invalid.
# Save the page. An error will be displayed explaining the broken style
# Edit the page in the rich text editor.
# Click the Wiki Markup tab. The content of the panel will be missing

